Package wtf.file.api.metadata

Schnittstelle MetadataContainer

Alle bekannten Unterschnittstellen:
EditableMetadataContainer
public interface MetadataContainer
Represents a container for metadata. This container allows for the retrieval and inspection of metadata elements identified by keys.

  • Methodendetails

    • has

      boolean has(String key)
      Checks if the metadata container contains a value associated with the specified key.
      Parameter:
      key - the key to check for existence in the metadata container
      Gibt zurück:
      true if a value associated with the specified key exists, false otherwise

    • keys

      List<String> keys()
      Retrieves a list of all keys present in the metadata container.
      Gibt zurück:
      a list of strings representing all keys in the metadata container

    • get

      String get(String key)
      Retrieves the value associated with the specified key in the metadata container.
      Parameter:
      key - the key for which the associated value is to be retrieved
      Gibt zurück:
      the value associated with the specified key, or null if no value is present

    • asMap

      Map<String,String> asMap()
      Retrieves all metadata elements as a map where the keys represent metadata keys and the values represent their corresponding metadata values.
      Gibt zurück:
      a map containing all metadata elements, with keys as metadata keys and values as metadata values
